											<h1 dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.6799999999999995;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:23pt;padding:0pt 0pt 7.5pt 0pt;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;color:#0a0a0a;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">IBRAND AFRICA LIMITED (&ldquo;ibrandafrica&rdquo;, &ldquo;we&rdquo;, &ldquo;us&rdquo; or &ldquo;our&rdquo;) is committed to protecting and respecting your personal information and your privacy.</span></h1>
